{"tid":1270982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府賀中共70週年嘅特備展覽，將會於7月3日隆重開幕！","createTime":"2019-07-01T04:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T04:37:52.000Z","uid":38055,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"214ee5d589ca3d6a2b1dc357c1a1962639fca20e","tid":1270982,"uid":38055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"借朋友account 一用<br />\n<br />\n特區政府賀中共70週年嘅特備展覽，將會於7月3日隆重開幕！<br />\n<br />\n按照其他展覽嘅慣例即係早一日（7月2日）係開幕典禮嘅大日子，勢必會有政府高官甚至係中央當局嘅官員出席<br />\n<br />\n我覺得而家開始要召集定所有會留守嘅巴絲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">71遊行完結後，諗個辦法去歷史博物館附近</span><br />\n<br />\n我唔鼓勵大家非法集結或者堵塞博物館出入口，影響到開幕亦都會令到中央冇面<br />\n<br />\n尤其有幾個位係千祈唔可以堵塞：<br />\n歷史博物館正門<br />\n歷史博物館職員入口<br />\n科學館正門<br />\n科學館職員入口<br />\n科學館/歷史博物館車場入口<br />\n<br />\n但係作為愛國愛港人士，提早一日去等待公眾開幕，係香港市民嘅應有責任<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好圍呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9099d7c95b104ccad1aaf8691965a4449b7df1","tid":1270982,"uid":38055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96bf5a6f9670136d174b83b571589554d7cc224d","tid":1270982,"uid":38055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d097c4bf3fe3e74f6f047c34ecef427126c90d9c","tid":1270982,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efbc8e318095284c7edbc5c85031b4209888113","tid":1270982,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ab5c82da8cfa92b718c165db0dd0786d4174ec","tid":1270982,"uid":38055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:22:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dbd